Board of Directors
The Mission of the corporation is to enhance the quality of life in Maple leaf Estates; to maintain a position of leadership among manufactured home communities by providing superior facilities, services, amenities, and management; and to operate the park as an “older person’s community”.
The leadership to guide the accomplishment of these goals, to evaluate future opportunities, and to provide competence and commitment, resides with the Corporation’s elected Board of Directors. Operation of the park in accordance with the Board’s approved policies is assigned to the General Manager.
